			<h3>HOW IT WORKS</h3>			  <div class="region region-left">
    <div id="block-menu-block-1" class="block block-menu-block">

    
  <div class="content">
    <div class="menu-block-wrapper menu-block-1 menu-name-menu-main-navigation parent-mlid-0 menu-level-2">
  <ul class="menu"><li class="first leaf active-trail active menu-mlid-349"><a href="45" title="What Happens When I Start Using ROGAINE® Products?" class="what-happens-when active-trail active">What Happens When I<br>Start Using ROGAINE<sup>&reg;</sup> Products?</a></li>
